# Install Script Checksums

This file contains SHA256 checksums for the install script. Verify your download before running:

```bash
# Download
curl -fsSL drx4.xyz/install -o /tmp/install.sh

# Verify (replace with actual checksum from release)
echo "<checksum>  /tmp/install.sh" | sha256sum -c -

# If verification passes, run
sh /tmp/install.sh
```

