## Why verify?

The install script has full control over your agent setup. Verifying the checksum ensures:
- You're running the official script
- The file wasn't tampered with in transit
- Supply chain integrity for production agents

For high-security deployments, also consider:
- Running in a VM or container
- Reviewing the script source before execution
- Using a dedicated agent machine (not your primary computer)